  <h3>3. WHAT PERSONAL DATA MAY WE COLLECT?</h3>
  <p>We may collect the following personal data about you:<br>The personal details you provide (such as name, address, e-mail address; business address and phone number) when submitting a membership application.<br>Information about your debit/credit card and bank account information that we require for the purpose of recording and processing your membership application (and administering your membership). For further details please also refer to the section below headed PAYMENT INFORMATION.<br>Personal details you choose to give when corresponding with us by phone, e-mail or that you provide to us when you participate in one of our events.<br>We may also receive other personal or private information about you that you choose to submit to this Site or any other websites we operate.</p>
